cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.GR 

This paper proposes a method for estimating room layouts of indoor scenes using convolutional neural networks and optimization techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also mentions the use of deep learning and end-to-end training, which suggests the possibility of belonging to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The optimization technique used in the paper is inspired by physics, which could place it in the category of cs.RO (Robotics) or cs.GR (Graphics).
